      • IdentifierManager

        public IdentifierManager(long lowerbound,
                         long upperbound)
        Parameters:
        lowerbound - the lower limit of the id-range to manage. Must be greater than or equal to MIN_ID.(下限-要管理的id范围的下限。必须大于或等于Min_ID。)
        upperbound - the upper limit of the id-range to manage. Must be less then or equal MAX_ID.(上限-要管理的id范围的上限。必须小于或等于MAX_ID。)

        Returns:

        Throws:

      • release

        public boolean release(long id)
        Parameters:
        id - the identifier to release. Must be greater than or equal to lowerbound and must be less than or equal to upperbound(id -要释放的标识符。必须大于或等于下限并且必须小于或等于上限)
        Returns:
        true, if the identifier was reserved and has been successfully released, false, if the identifier was not reserved.(如果标识符已被保留并且已成功释放，则为真;如果标识符未被保留，则为假。)
